statements: SELECT * FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts;
SELECT part_name, inspector_name FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts;
SELECT part_id, part_name, inspection_date FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts ORDER BY inspection_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts WHERE dimensions_3d_printed > 100;
SELECT part_id, part_name, inspector_name FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts WHERE inspector_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts;
SELECT part_name, dimensions_3d_printed FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts WHERE inspection_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY inspection_date DESC;
SELECT inspector_name, COUNT(*) AS inspection_count FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts GROUP BY inspector_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT part_name, ROUND(dimensions_3d_printed, 1) AS rounded_dimensions FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts WHERE dimensions_3d_printed BETWEEN 5.0 AND 7.0 ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT inspector_name FROM quality_control_data_3d_printed_parts WHERE inspector_name LIKE '%John%' ORDER BY inspector_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM Parts;
SELECT part_name, material FROM Parts WHERE part_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Inspections WHERE pass = true;
SELECT part_name, material, printer_model FROM Parts ORDER BY part_name DESC;
SELECT part_name, material, production_date FROM Parts WHERE printer_model = 'HP LaserJet';
SELECT part_id, part_name, material FROM Parts WHERE printer_model = 'XYZ-100' ORDER BY production_date DESC;
SELECT part_name, inspector_name, pass FROM Parts INNER JOIN Inspections ON Parts.part_id = Inspections.part_id WHERE pass = TRUE ORDER BY inspection_date ASC;
SELECT part_id, printer_model, COUNT(*) AS total_inspections FROM Parts LEFT JOIN Inspections ON Parts.part_id = Inspections.part_id GROUP BY part_id, printer_model ORDER BY total_inspections DESC;

SELECT part_id, part_name, material, inspection_date FROM Parts INNER JOIN Inspections ON Parts.part_id = Inspections.part_id WHERE inspector_name = 'John Doe' AND material LIKE 'Steel%' ORDER BY inspection_date DESC;

SELECT part_id, part_name, inspector_name, pass FROM Parts INNER JOIN Inspections ON Parts.part_id = Inspections.part_id WHERE inspection_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY inspector_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM QualityControlData ORDER BY inspection_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT part_name, inspection_result FROM QualityControlData WHERE inspection_result = 'Pass';
SELECT part_name, inspection_result FROM QualityControlData WHERE inspection_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM QualityControlData WHERE part_name LIKE 'B%';
SELECT PartImages.image_url, InspectionNotes.notes FROM PartImages JOIN InspectionNotes ON PartImages.part_id = InspectionNotes.part_id;
SELECT id, part_name, inspection_date, inspection_result FROM QualityControlData WHERE inspection_result = 'Pass' ORDER BY inspection_date DESC, part_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, part_name, inspection_date, inspection_result FROM QualityControlData WHERE part_name LIKE 'B%' AND inspection_result = 'Fail' ORDER BY part_name ASC, inspection_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT QualityControlData.*, PartImages.image_url, PartImages.image_description FROM QualityControlData LEFT JOIN PartImages ON QualityControlData.id = PartImages.part_id WHERE PartImages.image_url IS NOT NULL ORDER BY QualityControlData.id ASC LIMIT 3;

SELECT QualityControlData.part_name, InspectionNotes.notes FROM QualityControlData INNER JOIN InspectionNotes ON QualityControlData.id = InspectionNotes.part_id ORDER BY QualityControlData.part_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT part_name) AS unique_parts, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM QualityControlData;
SELECT * FROM PartQualityControl WHERE inspection_result = TRUE;
SELECT part_name, inspection_date FROM PartQualityControl WHERE inspector_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT id, part_name, inspection_date FROM PartQualityControl WHERE inspection_date >= '2023-01-01';
SELECT tool_name, manufacturer, calibration_date FROM InspectionTools WHERE manufacturer = 'ABC Company';
SELECT id, part_name, image_url FROM PartImages WHERE part_name = 'Component A';
SELECT part_name, inspection_date, inspector_name, inspection_result FROM PartQualityControl WHERE inspection_result = true;
SELECT part_name, image_url, image_description FROM PartImages ORDER BY image_url ASC;
SELECT part_name, geometry_data FROM PartGeometry WHERE id IN (1, 2, 3) AND part_name ILIKE 'A%' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT tool_name, manufacturer, calibration_date FROM InspectionTools WHERE calibration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, part_name, inspection_result FROM PartQualityControl WHERE inspector_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM QualityControlData;
SELECT part_id, inspector_name FROM QualityControlData WHERE inspection_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT result, part_id FROM QualityControlData WHERE inspector_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM 3DPrintedParts ORDER BY part_name ASC;
SELECT part_id, material_type FROM 3DPrintedParts WHERE print_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28';
SELECT part_id, inspection_date, inspector_name, result FROM QualityControlData;
SELECT * FROM 3DPrintedParts WHERE material_type = 'ABS' ORDER BY print_date DESC;
SELECT log_id, part_name, inspection_date, result FROM 3DPrintedParts JOIN InspectionLogs ON 3DPrintedParts.part_id = InspectionLogs.part_id;

SELECT inspector_name, inspector_phone, COUNT(log_id) AS total_inspections FROM Inspectors JOIN InspectionLogs ON Inspectors.inspector_id = InspectionLogs.inspector_id GROUP BY inspector_name, inspector_phone;

SELECT PartMeasurements.part_id, part_name, dimension_name, dimension_value FROM PartMeasurements JOIN 3DPrintedParts ON PartMeasurements.part_id = 3DPrintedParts.part_id WHERE dimension_value > 10 ORDER BY part_id ASC, dimension_value DESC;
